title: Amiga Paula does XM: Daxx - Secret Kind of Love 2 (A1200🎧Dolbyfied)
description:
"Secret Kind of Love [The Second Version]" by Daxx/Ravebusters (Bert Brüggemann). Art "Shion" by Optic/Focus Design^Desire^Planet Jazz, 2nd at Gerp 2016.

Made using real A1200 Rev. 1D.4 audio. Playback from DeliTracker 2.34 with 14Bit-NotePlayer 4.30:
- 14-bit calibrated Paula output
- Normal mixing with 42224 Hz mixing frequency
- No panning, no 3D and DSP off. Anti-click disabled
- Module reports 32 channels
- 100% flawless playback not guaranteed (the XM replayer is not perfect)

Visit my channel for more Amiga music.
